dct_description_sm: John C. Smock, State Geologist, C.C. Vermeule, topographer.
Relief map is accompanied by "Name sheet," in 3 sections, with note : "Localities may be identified on the Relief Map by laying this sheet over it in proper position."
At head of title: Geological survey of New Jersey.
